body:
### Attempt consult
First attempt to generate the website. In order to do a website it is necessary to follow these steps:

## 1. Create repository
We need to create a repository with the name attemptconsult.github.io

## 2. Publish website
Publish it under setting using launch as website. We will have our own mkdn for the website.

## 3. Personalize
Use the necessary elements to customize the website. I found a good source of information on
[these videos](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qoQzIjGbfTg)
